Sandpiper Crossing. How are you?

312
00:22:00,486 --> 00:22:02,454
Quite well, thank you.

313
00:22:02,655 --> 00:22:05,204
<i>- How</i> are <i>you?
- Doing fine. Doing fine.</i>

314
00:22:05,407 --> 00:22:07,751
