he wasn't himself, okay?

461
00:33:07,777 --> 00:33:09,154
This is good for him.

462
00:33:10,906 --> 00:33:13,750
<i>- Okay.
- What?</i>

463
00:33:13,950 --> 00:33:17,454
<i>I don't know. I'm just-- Whatever.
